{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "food-traceability-customers",
    "name": "Food Traceability - Customers 模块",
    "description": "食品安全溯源系统 - 消费者端接口测试集合\n\n基础URL: http://localhost:8081\n\n包含:\n  - 投诉管理: 提交/分页查询/详情/反馈\n  - 溯源查询: 扫码查询/记录扫码事件\n\n使用前请确保:\n  1. MySQL 已启动 (localhost:3306)\n  2. fts 数据库已创建，表已初始化\n  3. Spring Boot 应用已启动 (./mvnw spring-boot:run)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8081",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "batch_no",
      "value": "BATCH-20260623-001",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "complaint_id",
      "value": "1",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "投诉管理",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "提交投诉 - 正常",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"productBatchNo\": \"BATCH-20260623-001\",\n  \"productName\": \"有机奶粉\",\n  \"consumerName\": \"张三\",\n  \"consumerPhone\": \"13800138000\",\n  \"complaintType\": 1,\n  \"complaintTitle\": \"产品包装破损\",\n  \"complaintContent\": \"收到产品时发现外包装严重破损，内部密封已破裂\",\n  \"imageUrls\": \"https://img.example.com/1.jpg,https://img.example.com/2.jpg\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/complaint/submit",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "complaint", "submit"]
            },
            "description": "提交一条新的消费者投诉。投诉编号由系统自动生成（格式: TS + yyyyMMdd + 5位随机数）。\n\ncomplaintType 取值: 1-包装问题, 2-质量问题, 3-虚假宣传, 4-过期问题, 5-其他\n\nstatus 初始值为 0（待处理）"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "提交投诉 - 参数校验失败",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"productBatchNo\": \"BATCH-001\",\n  \"consumerPhone\": \"12345\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/complaint/submit",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "complaint", "submit"]
            },
            "description": "测试 Jakarta Validation 校验：\n- 缺少必填字段 (productName, consumerName, complaintType, complaintTitle, complaintContent)\n- 手机号格式不正确 (12345 不匹配正则 ^1[3-9]\\d{9}$)\n\n应返回 code=400，message 中列出所有字段错误"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "分页查询投诉",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"status\": 0,\n  \"pageNum\": 1,\n  \"pageSize\": 10\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/complaint/page",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "complaint", "page"]
            },
            "description": "分页查询投诉列表。支持可选筛选条件:\n- complaintNo: 投诉编号\n- productBatchNo: 产品批次号\n- consumerPhone: 消费者电话\n- complaintType: 投诉类型\n- status: 处理状态 (0-待处理, 1-处理中, 2-已反馈, 3-已关闭)\n- pageNum: 页码 (默认1)\n- pageSize: 每页条数 (默认10)\n\n结果按 createTime 倒序排列"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "查看投诉详情",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/complaint/detail/{{complaint_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "complaint", "detail", "{{complaint_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "根据投诉ID查看投诉详细信息。\n\n如果ID不存在，返回 code=500, message='投诉记录不存在'"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "处理投诉反馈",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"complaintId\": 1,\n  \"feedbackContent\": \"已联系消费者致歉并安排补发，消费者表示满意\",\n  \"feedbackBy\": \"客服管理员\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/complaint/feedback",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "complaint", "feedback"]
            },
            "description": "对投诉进行反馈处理。系统将自动:\n- 设置 status = 2 (已反馈)\n- 记录 feedbackContent, feedbackBy, feedbackTime"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "溯源查询",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "扫码查询溯源",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"productBatchNo\": \"{{batch_no}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/traceability/query",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "traceability", "query"]
            },
            "description": "根据产品批次号查询完整的溯源链路信息。\n\n返回数据包括:\n- 产品基本信息 (名称、规格、生产厂家、产地、生产日期、保质期)\n- 溯源节点列表 (按 sortOrder 升序排列)\n  - 包含节点名称、描述、时间、地点、操作人\n\n查询成功的同时会自动记录一条扫码记录。\n\n如果批次号不存在，返回 code=500, message='未找到该批次产品的溯源信息'"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "查询不存在的批次",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"productBatchNo\": \"BATCH-NOT-EXIST\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/traceability/query",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "traceability", "query"]
            },
            "description": "测试查询不存在的批次号，应返回 500 错误"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "记录扫码事件",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"productBatchNo\": \"{{batch_no}}\",\n  \"scanIp\": \"192.168.1.100\",\n  \"scanLocation\": \"北京市朝阳区\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/traceability/scan",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "traceability", "scan"]
            },
            "description": "独立记录扫码事件。scanIp 和 scanLocation 为可选字段。\n\n注意: /api/traceability/query 接口在查询溯源时也会自动记录扫码，无需单独调用此接口。"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
